Ivan Bonar https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ivan_Bonar 0 Ivan Eugene Bonar (October 31, 1924 – December 8, 1988) was an American character actor whose career in Hollywood, in films and television, spanned four decades, from the mid 1950s into the 1980s.
